      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Our father it is who writes to the brothers of the poll tax, (saying): "Receive a solidus worth of wine through the sons of Psashe, the men of the monk Jeremias of Pmanbete." Written Phamenoth 11, indiction 8. Elias.";(2nd hd.) "Daniel."</ab>
